The paper discusses the changing landscape of cloud computing infrastructure, which is primarily related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and networking (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the impact of these changes on various areas such as service space and self-learning systems, which fall under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the need for new computing architectures, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
